{"tid":2275132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中日網民罵戰，中國體操隊著防疫保護衣赴日，日網民寸太誇張","createTime":"2020-11-07T02:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T03:50:08.000Z","uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"512f91ea875b53d0b55e296cf9e79f67f1ec1539","tid":2275132,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0s0Y2jB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0s0Y2jB.png&h=5de2a132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐全球，中國體操代表團團員前晚（5日）抵達東京成田機場，出席四國體操邀請賽時被傳媒拍到穿上「全副武裝」，即時引起網民熱議。有網民直言，中國代表團不尊重日本，更有人認為代表團成員離開日本前都要穿着保護衣。<br />\n<br />\n中國代表團於周四晚抵達成田機場時，被傳媒拍到運動員和工作人員，除了佩戴口罩，更穿上全套防護服、眼罩及手套，而美國和俄羅斯代表團，卻僅戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n中國代表團的打扮，引起中日網民熱議，有人認為中國人只是為了保護自己及日本人，避免不必要的傳染，亦有中國網民稱：「日本是疫區」。日本網民反擊，對中國體操隊冷嘲熱諷，有人更稱：「我以為這是核事故的照片」、「你真的很害怕嗎？」、「很恐怖，這麼驚慌就不要來。」、「太不尊重日本了」。有人更用上幪面超人555的造型，諷刺中國代表團。<br />\n<br />\n裡面有影片及更詳盡內文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201107/3R57X6ADJND7DHHJ6LKLTXURBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201107%2F3R57X6ADJND7DHHJ6LKLTXURBY%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=66cc0b56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201107%2F3R57X6ADJND7DHHJ6LKLTXURBY%2F&h=4737914a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201107/3R57X6ADJND7DHHJ6LKLTXURBY/</a>"},{"pid":"0b91475cb9697086effdee705d102cb7a17623bb","tid":2275132,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgN8E8j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgN8E8j.png&h=63c03c01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e78fffee7076c367be99447793f2a75df81a725","tid":2275132,"uid":35776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:56:49.000Z","msg":"可能真係保護緊日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" clas